1243
00:55:32,700 --> 00:55:37,260
what if we could reflect
sunlight back into to space,

1244
00:55:37,260 --> 00:55:40,330
as a temporary measure
to help cool the Arctic,

1245
00:55:40,330 --> 00:55:43,140
while solutions like
decarbonization and carbon

1246
00:55:43,140 --> 00:55:45,510
