1287
00:57:40,730 --> 00:57:45,780
So it had a cooling effect while
also increasing air pollution,

1288
00:57:45,780 --> 00:57:47,150
not great.

1289
00:57:47,150 --> 00:57:51,140
But the idea is, what if we
